metadata.name: Primadonna
metadata.description:
Bathed in gold light at the edge of the bed, she sits stiffly like a poised doll. The hearts hoodie, a reference to Megan Fox’s character in Jennifer’s Body, is draped over her head in similar fashion to the The Virgin Mary’s veil. This image is beautifully haunting, echoing the unattainable standards women are often bent into. 

Laura Pieri shot on 35mm film wearing Gucci and Agent Provocateur 

The winner of this auction will receive a full size 1/1 print along with a custom frame and creative media analysis done by the artists.
